446
00:31:49,609 --> 00:31:53,559
You're right. It's going down well, now.

447
00:31:53,559 --> 00:31:56,459
It's so quiet in the house.

448
00:31:56,459 --> 00:31:58,199
Is it because it's at the end of the street?

449
00:31:58,199 --> 00:32:00,999
All my children moved out.

450
00:32:00,999 --> 00:32:04,799
My husband and I moved here, just the two of us.

451
00:32:04,799 --> 00:32:07,939
It's quiet and peaceful.

452
00:32:07,939 --> 00:32:09,769
It's really great.

453
00:32:09,769 --> 00:32:13,549
Only old people like me live in this area.

454
00:32:13,549 --> 00:32:16,149
Thanks to you, it's much better.

455
00:32:16,149 --> 00:32:19,749
How much do I owe you?

456
00:32:46,649 --> 00:32:48,109
My apologies.

457
00:32:48,109 --> 00:32:51,649
Is there anything else I can help you with?

458
00:32:54,759 --> 00:32:59,019
Well, what do you mean?

459
00:32:59,019 --> 00:33:01,819
You fixed this perfectly.

460
00:33:01,849 --> 00:33:03,589
The payment...

461
00:33:03,589 --> 00:33:07,769
will be what I told you over the phone, ma'am.
